T1  - Investment Adjustment Costs: An Empirical Assessment
AU  - GROTH, CHARLOTTA
AU  - KHAN, HASHMAT
Y1  - 2010/12/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/12/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1538-4616.2010.00350.x
